Package org.gradoop.flink.model.api.operators

Contains all operator interface used in the Gradoop framework.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ApplicableUnaryGraphToGraphOperator
    A marker interface for instances of UnaryGraphToGraphOperator that support the application on each element in a graph collection.
    BinaryCollectionToCollectionOperator
    Creates a GraphCollection based on two input collections.
    BinaryCollectionToValueOperator<T>
    Creates a (usually 1-element) Boolean dataset based on two input graphs.
    BinaryGraphToGraphOperator
    Creates a LogicalGraph based on two input graphs.
    BinaryGraphToValueOperator<T>
    Creates a (usually 1-element) Boolean dataset based on two input graphs.
    GraphCollectionGenerator
    Generates a graph collection
    GraphGenerator
    Generates a logical graph
    GraphsToGraphOperator
    Creates a LogicalGraph based on an at least one input graph.
    GraphTransactionsGenerator
    Generates a set of graph transactions
    GraphTransactionsOperators
    Describes all operators that can be applied on a single logical graph in the EPGM.
    Operator
    Base interface for all EPGM operators.
    ReducibleBinaryGraphToGraphOperator
    A marker interface for instances of BinaryGraphToGraphOperator that support the reduction of a collection to a single logical graph.
    UnaryBaseGraphToBaseGraphOperator<LG extends BaseGraph>
    Creates a graph of type LG based on one input graph of the same type.
    UnaryBaseGraphToValueOperator<G extends BaseGraph,V>
    Creates a value of type V from one input graph of type G.
    UnaryCollectionToCollectionOperator
    Creates a GraphCollection based on one input collection.
    UnaryCollectionToGraphOperator
    Creates a LogicalGraph from one input collection.
    UnaryGraphCollectionToValueOperator<T>
    Creates a value from one input collection.
    UnaryGraphToCollectionOperator
    Creates a GraphCollection based on one LogicalGraph.
    UnaryGraphToGraphOperator
    Creates a LogicalGraph based on one input LogicalGraph.
    UnaryGraphToValueOperator<T>
    Creates a value from one input LogicalGraph.

Package org.gradoop.flink.model.api.operators Description
